  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=010ba632&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2F0m9F5vC1OGiaYLKsJCOl8OYbf6KCs6ITZ3Emaxc9ak1edrNVA6TD1leRVB5ZUao0qSOEdFNusjnSO59klo69JPa2boXaURpSFSiclWvDJMXsE%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\" style=\"font-size: 1rem;\"></p>\n  <div style=\"font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif;font-size: 15px;line-height: 1.75;text-align: left;\">\n   <blockquote style=\"border-radius:6px;border-top:0.2px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);padding:1em 1em 1em 2em;border-right:0.2px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-left:4px solid #FA5151;margin-top:0 !important;font-style:italic;margin-bottom:1em;border-bottom:0.2px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);\">\n    <p style=\"margin:0;display:block;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:1em;\"><span leaf=\"\">可能是目前体验最丝滑，生态打通程度最高的🦞</span></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <h2 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"display: table;margin: 4em auto 2em;color: #fff;background: #FA5151;font-weight: bold;text-align: center;padding: 0.3em 1.2em;font-size: 19.5px;border-radius: 8px 24px 8px 24px;box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);\"><span leaf=\"\">开通ArkClaw</span></h2>\n   <span leaf=\"\">访问： <a href=\"https://www.volcengine.com/product/arkclaw\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.volcengine.com/product/arkclaw</a> ，单击“立即订阅”按钮。</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n    <br> \n   </span>\n   <figure style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"eDWgq7\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5472222222222223\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\";\" data-imgfileid=\"100011075\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7a9c81df&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F0m9F5vC1OGh3oc8FWKX3hT4ZXjJibad01uHCbZAD2xELKajkF7KLQVwI3QjSZKpmQA34Tpiafk3OaWlcTpFENFKIibRq5tEx5icWJrUOibmHwIfc%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n   </figure>\n   <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;\"><span leaf=\"\">选择一个适合自己的订阅plan，单击“立即订阅”按钮</span></p>\n   <blockquote style=\"border-radius:6px;border-top:0.2px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);padding:1em 1em 1em 2em;border-right:0.2px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-left:4px solid #FA5151;font-style:italic;margin-bottom:1em;border-bottom:0.2px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);\">\n    <p style=\"margin:0;display:block;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:1em;\"><span leaf=\"\">注意：</span><code style=\"font-size: 90%;color: #d14;background: rgba(27, 31, 35, 0.05);padding: 3px 5px;border-radius: 4px;\"><span leaf=\"\">ArkClaw订阅自带火山引擎的Coding Plan</span></code><span leaf=\"\">（方便了，但成本也会高一些）</span></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <figure style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"YiOGMn\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5472222222222223\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\";\" data-imgfileid=\"100011080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=58c43872&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F0m9F5vC1OGjfSMdUznTjXEIIlGcsRG3cY6EdjZTRFY8lZBZUOYRejGBmB7KZKGUSkEyLasfY80a4R1OZwS9G42LZXnRyUPibfIPUUPo0k1BE%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n   </figure>\n   <span leaf=\"\">如果没有单独买过Coding Plan，直接弹出扫码支付窗口：</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n    <br> \n   </span>\n   <figure style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"eBc7jW\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.575925925925926\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\";\" data-imgfileid=\"100011082\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0d1ed42e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F0m9F5vC1OGjDnuELicg0DOrm4rIOuibEf1KbZMoGPk3aRwfFeibiaHl745qmSlFuyMDaJD9B27jqZlsVeaDicdlUX869AyHqQr7MIGibXCB58USRI%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n   </figure>\n   <span leaf=\"\">如果单独买过Coding Plan，则进入一个以Coding Plan截止日期折算服务器成本的购买页面：</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n    <br> \n   </span>\n   <figure style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"qlP3dM\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5462962962962963\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\";\" data-imgfileid=\"100011079\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ea9c8cfe&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F0m9F5vC1OGjC4srBm3nXQRw8XT1AHNkjgCuSpQPWY59rl3ms38gROLGbsmgW0zA8HkWiaIhMTwAbJIenqbVe0jiatdd7jPRr9q5FIRPtYNSOk%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n   </figure>\n   <span leaf=\"\">购买完成之后，ArkClaw进入部署和启动阶段：</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n    <br> \n   </span>\n   <figure style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"Is0lEr\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5462962962962963\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\";\" data-imgfileid=\"100011078\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8d530044&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F0m9F5vC1OGgj46zkqHkNgE0jruEJTopdicokrxBQoDxFCeicRsgMLE1MibYf3V2LfmjRgk77nDZSCMz2lfddUgldeNiaUXEHiakRLHLSmTp8mK2A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n   </figure>\n   <span leaf=\"\">2分钟之后，你就可以和ArkClaw进行首次对话了（Bootstrap）</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n    <br> \n   </span>\n   <figure style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"pPSGX3\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5138888888888888\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\";\" data-imgfileid=\"100011077\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=435e8fc1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F0m9F5vC1OGjiaoA6ic2s8Yuc4VocmC2ibecBPD7qSmYbiaSvSKXmahTkQeldS0se3PqK1icunslDDq1Zrr0CibRQWZZAzA62zHSiap2qPU5eVRViaGo%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n   </figure>\n   <span leaf=\"\">ArkClaw默认的模型是所谓的</span><code style=\"font-size: 90%;color: #d14;background: rgba(27, 31, 35, 0.05);padding: 3px 5px;border-radius: 4px;\"><span leaf=\"\">ark/ark-code-latest</span></code><span leaf=\"\">。如果希望切换Coding Plan中的其他模型，操作步骤如下：</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n    <br> \n   </span>\n   <figure style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"sdtLFw\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5481481481481482\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\";\" data-imgfileid=\"100011092\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f3eed0ed&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F0m9F5vC1OGiaZDcKiapuJSsyGQIsY2OkiaJs0RCgVVeXRJSWicZ9SGX1evnZia0AJoRb8FlRLnjkqHtib9zJ9YR5HyuAs9Oia8pNly8fDa2MVaBJkQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n   </figure>\n   <figure style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img alt=\"Ry3Mfq\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100011101\" data-ratio=\"0.5472222222222223\" style=\";\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=cee09f36&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F0m9F5vC1OGgWthFqWl9WmyMXmM9hkbVmALqjGwLbs7TKqvE2B6FKwOpXPxeIIroBNTaOQsqquOibwq9V72bvhdldENu7ZAFK1JqTG2DicX3q4%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n   </figure>\n   <span leaf=\"\"> \n    <br> \n   </span><span leaf=\"\">然后选择自己喜欢的模型即可。你也可以选择“模型广场”中的模型，不过这里是按照token单独收费的，建议使用“Coding Plan”中的模型即可。</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n    <br> \n   </span>\n   <figure style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img alt=\"m8csrQ\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100011090\" data-ratio=\"0.5481481481481482\" style=\";\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b15bfe40&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F0m9F5vC1OGhfhjkmIaKXxBictB3qmkQsFXQBYSwgJZ20iavX25GYiaaRx7yKGkTCRbbZDiaiaCslCXrWMPTcNOCIfsGHQv6qw8bh7DWkDia9xn22c%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n   </figure>\n   <span leaf=\"\">切换了模型之后，会有1分钟左右的切换和重启Gateway的时间：</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n    <br> \n   </span>\n   <figure style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img alt=\"9Se0hW\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100011089\" data-ratio=\"0.5462962962962963\" style=\";\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f0fe2b2c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F0m9F5vC1OGjAmI3WK2rzX37JnbiaficgdvOmEYXWxaHHUMasIHtxAknjv4eb0x2z31wODPGb3gCkib3VxdUAOX82ibhPiagqOXk7iaePl9iajAicQVQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n   </figure>\n   <span leaf=\"\">切换完成之后，你可以问它&nbsp;</span><code style=\"font-size: 90%;color: #d14;background: rgba(27, 31, 35, 0.05);padding: 3px 5px;border-radius: 4px;\"><span leaf=\"\">你现在是什么LLM？</span></code><span leaf=\"\">，它应当可以正确显示你使用的新模型（见红线部分）：</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n    <br> \n   </span>\n   <figure style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img alt=\"GOZ94y\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100011087\" data-ratio=\"0.5472222222222223\" style=\";\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=61af104d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F0m9F5vC1OGjHia2hkDWQuKjTQgiakfHShv5ExYCy0ibiarlgxqk3KHicU3unr4rCAJGne93m0wo0hicdN1H6wztMTJPqlOpYBibSzn1IefAuYiccmUY%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n   </figure>\n   <h2 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"display: table;margin: 4em auto 2em;color: #fff;background: #FA5151;font-weight: bold;text-align: center;padding: 0.3em 1.2em;font-size: 19.5px;border-radius: 8px 24px 8px 24px;box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);\"><span leaf=\"\">打通飞书</span></h2>\n   <span leaf=\"\">单击对话窗口上方的“消息渠道”按钮</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n    <br> \n   </span>\n   <figure style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img alt=\"d9loUg\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100011084\" data-ratio=\"0.5453703703703704\" style=\";\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=185ecfdb&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%